    "description": "Monthly lifecycle manager: 1st of month 9 AM. For each LIVE product: checks Supabase signups, Stripe revenue, Sentry errors. Classifies: THRIVING/STABLE/STRUGGLING/FADING/SUNSET. Auto-sunsets failing products (60+ days, $0, 0 subs). Updates sheet, sends report email.",
